  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed development would, by reason of its height, bulk and design, appear as an unacceptably dominant and visually intrusive feature in the streetscene harmful to the character and appearance of the surrounding area and visual amenity of the locality contrary to Policy DC61 of the adopted London Borough of Havering's  LDF Core Strategy and Development Control Policies DPD 2008 and Havering Landscaping SPD 2011.",
